description: Price improvement! Welcome to Bigelow Square! The Bigelow was listed on the National Register of Historic Places in 1985. It is well maintained as are the patio and landscaped areas. This 1 bedroom condominium is warm, inviting and spacious. The new owner will enjoy a fantastic lifestyle with conveniences just steps away from their front door, including: the MBTA, supermarket, shops and restaurants. The condominium community is A+! 1 parking spot and storage unit are included. Laundry room on site.
